Package org.hibernate.reactive.dialect

Class ReactiveDialectWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hibernate.dialect.Dialect
      • org.hibernate.dialect.DialectDelegateWrapper
        • org.hibernate.reactive.dialect.ReactiveDialectWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FunctionContributor, TypeContributor, ConversionContext
    public final class ReactiveDialectWrapper
extends DialectDelegateWrapper
    Wraps the given dialect to make some internal components reactive; also, potentially applies a SQL syntax workaround if the wrapped Dialect is extending PostgreSQLDialect.
